title: Ryanair puts on extra flights for 6 Nations
text:
Thursday 27th August 2015 Ryanair puts on extra flights for 6 Nations 
Ryanair has added four extra flights between London and Edinburgh for the Scotland versus England 6 Nations clash at Murrayfield in February. Flights depart on February 6 at 07:55 and 10:55, returning on February 7 at 12:25 and 18:50. Ryanair has also scheduled extra flights for Italy versus England at the Stadio Olimpico later in the month. These depart on February 13 at 16:15 and 19:20, returning on February 15 at 06:45 and 16:25. 
Thursday, August 27, 2015
